		"Description": "@@#Color:Blue:Magical@@ is a @@#Color:Blue:Tag@@ bestowed upon a select number of @@#Color:Blue:Items@@ and  @@#Color:Blue:Pages@@ which are able harness Elemental Energies in the following forms:\n\n@@#Color:DmgColor:Cold@@ low variance with higher precision and capable of inflicting @@#EftDef:AilmentChilled@@ which can lead to @@#EftDef:AilmentFrozen@@.\n\n@@#Color:DmgColor:Fire@@ standard variance and easily applied over large areas, often inclicting @@#EftDef:AilmentBurned@@.\n\n@@#Color:DmgColor:Shock@@ high variance and diffult to control, occationally inflicting @@#EftDef:AilmentShocked@@.\n\n@@#Color:DmgColor:Poison@@ standard variance but less powerful, frequently inflicting various types of @@#Color:Blue:Poisons@@.",
		"DisplayName": "Magical"
